title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2010-12 Hyundai Genesis Coupe LED Tail Lights
description:
This video demonstrates how to install a set of Spyder custom aftermarket LED tail lights for the popular 2-door Hyundai Genesis Coupe. Follow along as we go through the installation, one step at a time.

Tools Required:
10mm Socket & Ratchet
tags: Spyder LED Tail Lights, Hyundai Genesis, how to install LED tail lights, spyder
